470&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n練下胸 可能會改善到</blockquote><br />\n點去練胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點樣練胸</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n問下你既健身教練 最多都係改善</blockquote><br />\nThx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f5a3ea2c17ab47a5480361bff8211ca1ec85d1","tid":229491,"uid":112464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:09:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 青春期食左某D野令荷爾蒙失調,令乳線過度發育,呢種要靠手術切除<br />\n2. 體脂高,呢種靠控制飲食同減肥就得<br />\n<br />\n建議你減到見到6舊腹肌先再諗係咪因為1</blockquote><br />\nThx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21597af6c5b5936bfe3c468c37bee539b7d9982f","tid":229491,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:12:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170429/56550718\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170429%2F56550718&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM34zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=5e0e12b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170429%2F56550718&h=2c60e647\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170429/56550718</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/EQoJO0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2FEQoJO0.jpg&h=8039d57a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無得減<br />\n一定要做手術<br />\n唔做手術你粒lin就係咁</blockquote><br />\n講佢又唔信，以為我地串佢肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/facelift/M.1234924961.A.22D.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2Ffacelift%2FM.1234924961.A.22D.html&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM34zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=94b75ee0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/facelift/M.1234924961.A.22D.html</a><br />\n「男性女乳症」的乳房無法藉著飲食控制或運動使其變小。「男性女乳症」依其形態，可<br />\n分為純粹的「乳腺增大」、單獨的「脂肪堆積」（又叫假性「男性女乳症」）以及「乳腺<br />\n增大伴隨脂肪堆積」等三種。純粹的「乳腺增大」需手術切除或刮除過大的乳腺；單獨的<br />\n「脂肪堆積」可藉抽脂治療；若是「乳腺增大伴隨脂肪堆積」，則需併用抽脂及乳腺組織<br />\n切除或刮除法。<br />\n接受現實啦 <br />\n你谷胸只會肌肉係底 對波係面整到自己越黎越凸<br />\n冇得救 做手術仲好 唔好浪費時間"},{"pid":"fdb81f112a70c14c91f82074f9a23acb33b8ceba","tid":229491,"uid":59886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:12:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6176a4f96d44b1e2b93198cc472b572fab00284","tid":229491,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:14:45.000Z","msg":"要怪就怪支那畜係d雞上面打雌激素<br />\n發育時期食左就會搞到你咁<br />\n要報仇去搵班畜牲就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61bd581ad6fded06be879c7da8c6f803c858dbde","tid":229491,"uid":112464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T16:26:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我本身少少肥底"}]}